(43, 5, 30, 19, 96, 13, 13, NULL, 'Judgment and Righteousness Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of judgment in both passages. John 5:30 emphasizes the just judgment of Jesus, while Psalms 96:13 speaks of the Lord judging the earth with righteousness.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
